        <Query Active="False" DisplayList="True" DisplayStat="False" DisplaySelectionView="False" IsCriticalRule="False"><![CDATA[// <Name>Check that the assembly Asm1 is only using the assemblies Asm2, Asm3 or mscorlib</Name>
